2023, were tentatively priced by a Goldman, Sachs &amp; Co. group
to yield from 6.35% in 1995 to 7.10% in 2010 and 2023.
Current interest serial bonds are priced at par to yield from
6.35% in 1995 to 7.00% in 2005. There are $12.5 million of 7%
